                        "data": "Sri Lanka's minimum wage rate is LKR 12,500 per month."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "title": "Individual Income Tax",
                "data": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "data": "The individual income tax ranges from 6% to 18%. Income tax is calculated according to progressive rates. Multiple additional factors may impact overall rates, such as household status and the number of children."
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "table",
                        "data": [
                            {
                                "Gross Annual Income": "Up to currency - LKR 3,000,000",
