                                "text": "Christmas Day (2 days)."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph",
                        "data": "In Sri Lanka, Poya Holidays are non-working days. As 70% of the residents are religious, the government takes these days as public holidays, as well as the ones listed above."
                    }
